WEBVTT

00:05:58.542 --> 00:06:02.833
I needed their support once again
if I was going to be successful.

00:06:03.708 --> 00:06:08.309
So I formed a community board
with religious leaders, parents

00:06:08.333 --> 00:06:11.559
and some teachers from other schools.

00:06:11.583 --> 00:06:15.434
I needed allies in the government
and in the community

00:06:15.458 --> 00:06:18.059
to help advance my goal.

00:06:18.083 --> 00:06:20.726
I needed especially
the support of the chief

00:06:20.750 --> 00:06:24.083
to help me enforce
the no-FGM policy in my school.

00:06:24.833 --> 00:06:27.476
At first he was resistant,

00:06:27.500 --> 00:06:28.768
but I persisted --

00:06:28.792 --> 00:06:30.059
(Laughter)